'''Dennis Phillips''' is the date Chandler's mom, [[Nora Bing]], brings to the wedding when [[Chandler Bing|Chandler]] marries [[Monica Geller|Monica]].  Dennis appears in "[[The One After I Do]]".  He is played by [[Jim Piddock]].
